posts.post_title: FS: Group of (5) T206 HOFs  (Matty, Evers, Crawford, Jennings).
posts.post_content:
Putting these up as a set for $550 pp gift shipped through the weekend. If no takers by Monday I'll split them up and sell separately. The Matty and Evers alone should cover the asking price.

Johnny Evers Portrait SGC 20
Johnny Evers With Bat Chicago On Shirt VG+. Great colors on this one.
Sam Crawford Throwing SGC 30
Hughie Jennings Both Hands PSA 1. The best-looking PSA 1 in my collection.
Christy Mathewson portrait SGC 10. Some paper loss.
